    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. The hemolysis prediction model demonstrates sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The methodology is consistent with published CFD hemolysis assessment practice as documented in the referenced literature including the hemolysis modeling review at https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ymeth.2024.03.003 which provides updated power-law coefficients adopted in this assessment. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion satisfied across all operating conditions. Assessment accepted for regulatory submission.",
